he wife of  Henry VI  of England,  Margaret of Anjou  (  1430–82 ), and of  Margaret Tudor  (  1489–1541 ), sister of  Henry VIII , who married James IV of Scotland and ruled as regent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."]},{"name":"Margarete","meanings":["from Greek.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margrethe","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Margaretha was born about 1562, in Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hesse, Germany. She married Hanß Michael Kumpft about 1594, in Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hesse, Germany. They were the parents of at least 3 sons. She died after 1618, in her hometown."},"et":{"about 1562–after 1618":"umbes 1562–pärast 1618","1560–1617":"1560–1617","1595–1631":"1595–1631","1600–1640":"1600–1640","–1626":"–1626","1562–1618":"1562–1618","after 1618":"pärast 1618","1560":"1560","1567":"1567","1600":"1600","1631":"1631","about 1600":"umbes 1600","1640":"1640","1595":"1595","1562":"1562","1618":"1618","about 1594":"umbes 1594","1617":"1617","about 1562":"umbes 1562","1945":"1945","1626":"1626","Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Germany":"Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Saksamaa","Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Deutschland":"Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Saksamaa"},"fi":{"about 1562–after 1618":"noin 1562–1618 jälkeen","1560–1617":"1560–1617","1595–1631":"1595–1631","1600–1640":"1600–1640","–1626":"–1626","1562–1618":"1562–1618","after 1618":"1618 jälkeen","1560":"1560","1567":"1567","1600":"1600","1631":"1631","about 1600":"noin 1600","1640":"1640","1595":"1595","1562":"1562","1618":"1618","about 1594":"noin 1594","1617":"1617","about 1562":"noin 1562","1945":"1945","1626":"1626","Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Germany":"Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Saksa","Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Deutschland":"Beerfelden, Odenwaldkreis, Hessen, Saksa"},"fr":{"about 1562–after 1618":"environ 1562–après 1618","1560–1617":"1560–1617","159